---

## 10) Renewal Readiness (90/60/30)
### 90 days before renewal
- [ ] Outcomes on track with evidence placeholders
- [ ] Stakeholder alignment confirmed (champion + decision maker)
- [ ] Renewal dependencies identified and planned

### 60 days before renewal
- [ ] Gaps have owners and dates
- [ ] Exec sponsor path confirmed if required
- [ ] Renewal path steps mapped (placeholders only)

### 30 days before renewal
- [ ] Proof pack ready (what changed, metrics, wins)
- [ ] Commercial path ready (placeholders only)
- [ ] Risk remaining is explicitly accepted or mitigated

